\c 121 
\m \bd Faarfannaa \bd*\bd 121\bd*
\s2 \bdit \zbr\bdit*Gargaarsi Waaqayyo Biraa Dhufuu Isaa (Weedduu ittiin ol ba'an)
\m \bd 1\bd* Iji koo gara gaarotaatti ol in ilaala, gargaarsi koo eessaa dhufa?
\m \bd 2\bd* Gargaarsi koo Waaqayyo biraa in dhufa; inni immoo isa bantiiwwan waaqaa, lafas uumee dha.
\m \bd 3\bd* Inni miilli kee akka sigigaatu hin godhu, inni si eegus hin mugu.
\m \bd 4\bd* Kunoo, inni Israa'elin eegu, matumaa hin mugu, hin rafus.
\m \bd 5\bd* Waaqayyo si eega, Waaqayyo gaaddisa kee ti, inni gara mirga kee jira.
\m \bd 6\bd* Guyyaa aduun si hin rukutu, halkanis ji'i si hin miidhu.
\m \bd 7\bd* Waaqayyo hamaa hundumaattii si eega, inni jireenya kee in eega.
\m \bd 8\bd* Waaqayyo gad ba'uu kee, ol galuu kees ammaa jalqabee hamma bara baraatti in eega.
\b 
